  "body": "\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nAs a developer I might have some contracts which need to be updated based on the storage location/slot not the state variable name (only owner). One of the problems that calculating the storage slot manually takes time and prone to the human error.\r\n\r\nI built a hardhat plugin which simply enables the compiler to generate the storage layout and print it in a nice way for all any contract inside the project. \r\n\r\nAttached a screenshot for it:\r\n\r\n```┌─────────────────┬────────────────┬──────────────┬────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\r\n│ contract        │ state_variable │ storage_slot │ offset │ type                                                │\r\n├─────────────────┼────────────────┼──────────────┼────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\r\n│ ERC20           │ _balances      │      0       │   0    │ t_mapping(t_address,t_uint256)                      │\r\n│ ERC20           │ _allowances    │      1       │   0    │ t_mapping(t_address,t_mapping(t_address,t_uint256)) │\r\n│ ERC20           │ _totalSupply   │      2       │   0    │ t_uint256                                           │\r\n│ ERC20           │ _name          │      3       │   0    │ t_string_storage                                    │\r\n│ ERC20           │ _symbol        │      4       │   0    │ t_string_storage                                    │\r\n│ WatermelonToken │ _balances      │      0       │   0    │ t_mapping(t_address,t_uint256)                      │\r\n│ WatermelonToken │ _allowances    │      1       │   0    │ t_mapping(t_address,t_mapping(t_address,t_uint256)) │\r\n│ WatermelonToken │ _totalSupply   │      2       │   0    │ t_uint256                                           │\r\n│ WatermelonToken │ _name          │      3       │   0    │ t_string_storage                                    │\r\n│ WatermelonToken │ _symbol        │      4       │   0    │ t_string_storage                                    │\r\n└─────────────────┴────────────────┴──────────────┴────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnother features to be done:\r\n- Specifying the contract name\r\n- Updating the storage slot with a new value (given the right privilege).\r\n",
